### Upload Image for Store (Requires Authentication)
### Use FormData with field name 'file'
POST {{baseUrl}}/stores/{{storeId}}/upload-image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer {{token_prestador}}

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="store-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
